functionDecorators.name: setERC165
functionDecorators.description: set or unset ERC165 using DiamondStorage.supportedInterfaces.

parameterDecorators.name: interfaceIds
parameterDecorators.description: list of interface id to set as supported.

parameterDecorators.name: interfaceIdsToRemove
parameterDecorators.description: list of interface id to unset as supported. Technically, you can remove support of ERC165 by having the IERC165 id itself being part of that array.
